OL,3,CAirline stops flight with medical
OL,4,Cpatients on to run private golf trip
OL,6,FPatients have missed medical
OL,7,Fappointments after they say their
OL,8,Fscheduled flight was cancelled to
OL,9,Fallow a group of golfers to privately
OL,10,Fcharter the plane instead.
OL,12,FThe Aurigny morning service on Friday
OL,13,F7 June had been set to transport
OL,14,Fpassengers from Alderney to Guernsey
OL,15,Fon a regular commercial route.
OL,17,FSome had important hospital visits
OL,18,Fplanned as part of a health agreement
OL,19,Fbetween the two islands.
