OL,6,FHowever, travellers say they learnt
OL,7,Ftheir flight was no longer going ahead
OL,8,Fonce they arrived at Alderney Airport
OL,9,Fto check-in.
OL,11,FInstead, they say the company chose to
OL,12,Fsend the plane to Jersey without any
OL,13,Fpassengers on so it could pick up
OL,14,Fgolfers and bring them to Alderney.
OL,16,FHelen Young was one of those affected
OL,17,Fand describes the situation as
OL,18,F"unacceptable".
