OL,6,FShe explains: "I had waited eight
OL,7,Fmonths for this appointment and the
OL,8,Ffact that it is very hard to get slots
OL,9,Fwith Aurigny in line with appointments
OL,10,Fmade it very frustrating.
OL,12,F"I arrived at the airport at seven in
OL,13,Fthe morning, I met the check-in people
OL,14,Fand they looked at me strangely. I
OL,15,Fsaid, 'I'm going to Guernsey on a
OL,16,Fmedical', they said, 'The first
OL,17,Frotation has been cancelled and it's
OL,18,Fgoing to Jersey on a charter'.
