OL,3,CAirline stops flight with medical
OL,4,Cpatients on to run private golf trip
OL,6,F"I was fuming. I was told we could be
OL,7,Fscheduled to go on the 12am flight but
OL,8,Fmy medical was for 11am so it wouldn't
OL,9,Fwork for me.
OL,11,F"The frustrating part of it all is
OL,12,Fthat we have to contend with the
OL,13,Fweather, Aurigny staff sickness,
OL,14,Fplanes going tech and medicals.
OL,16,F"None of those can be helped but when
OL,17,Fa scheduled flight is cancelled due to
OL,18,Fa chartered flight then that can be
OL,19,Fhelped.
