OL,6,F"It is unacceptable as far as I'm
OL,7,Fconcerned and this should not happen
OL,8,Fagain."
OL,10,FTwo Aurigny flights were scheduled for
OL,11,Faround the same time on Friday morning.
OL,13,FDue to staff shortages, Aurigny could
OL,14,Fonly crew one flight and chose to
OL,15,Fhonour the chartered service.
