OL,6,FWhilst the airline did not give me an
OL,7,Fanswer as to why this decision was
OL,8,Fmade, they did send over a statement
OL,9,Fwhich says: "It is not unusual for
OL,10,Fflight times to change when travelling
OL,11,Fbetween the islands and we apologise
OL,12,Ffor any inconvenience caused by the
OL,13,Fadjustment.
OL,15,F"As per our standard practice, all
OL,16,Fcustomers were informed of the change
OL,17,Fin advance."
OL,19,FHowever, passengers I've spoken to say
OL,20,Fthey only found out once they were
OL,21,Finside the airport.
