OL,6,FWe've reported multiple times over the
OL,7,Flast few months about travel delays
OL,8,Fand disruption due to several issues -
OL,9,Fsome out of Aurigny's control.
OL,11,FIt's unclear whether the airline knew
OL,12,Fthe impact cancelling this flight
OL,13,Fwould have but given it's already
OL,14,Funder some public pressure, this may
OL,15,Fnot help their reputation.
